  "anticipated_spec_changes": null,
  "security_risks": "The \"ttl\" can only extend the lifetime of a dictionary for responses that are otherwise cacheable but with a short (or zero) max-age. Responses that are not allowed to be stored in the HTTP cache (no-store or no-cache) will still not be used as a dictionary and can not be extended.",
